            "text": "Red line, nice overhang, start in double sidepulls/underclings, dyno from big holds to the top without the side edges.",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:turbo"
            ]
          }
        },
        "turbo-problem-14": {
